# UI/UX Design System

All UI work MUST follow these patterns. Read this before creating or modifying
any component, page, or style.

## Visual Identity

Dark-only glassmorphism aesthetic. No light mode, no theme toggle.
Root HTML element has `className="dark"`, body uses `color-scheme: dark`.

### Background

Full-viewport gradient on `body`:

```
linear-gradient(145deg, #0c0a1a 0%, #12102b 30%, #0e1628 60%, #0a0e1a 100%)
```

Atmospheric mesh layer (`bg-mesh` div in root layout) adds two blurred radial
gradient orbs: indigo (`#6366f1`) top-right, green (`#22c55e`) bottom-left, both
at 25% opacity with 120px blur.

## Color Tokens

All custom colors live in `app/globals.css` inside `@theme { }` (Tailwind v4).
Use these tokens via Tailwind utilities (e.g. `bg-glass`, `text-accent`).
Never introduce new hard-coded colors without adding them to `@theme` first.

