| Token | Value | Usage |
|-------|-------|-------|
| `glass` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.06)` | Default panel/card bg |
| `glass-border` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.1)` | Panel/card border |
| `glass-hover` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.1)` | Hover state bg |
| `glass-active` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.14)` | Active/pressed state bg |
| `glass-text` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.9)` | Primary text |
| `glass-text-muted` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.5)` | Secondary text, inactive tabs |
| `glass-text-dim` | `rgba(255,255,255, 0.35)` | Tertiary text, micro labels |

