## Glass Panel Classes

Three tiers defined in `globals.css`. Never invent new panel styles.

| Class | Radius | Blur | Use for |
|-------|--------|------|---------|
| `glass-panel` | 1rem | 20px, saturate 1.4 | Sections, containers, nav bar |
| `glass-panel-elevated` | 1rem | 24px, saturate 1.5, deep shadow + inset highlight | Hero blocks, modals, overlays |
| `glass-card` | 0.75rem | 16px, saturate 1.3, hover transition | Metric tiles, small interactive items |

### Panel composition rules

- Sections: `glass-panel p-4` or `glass-panel p-5`
- Stat cards: `glass-card p-3`
- Interactive cards: add `cursor-pointer hover:bg-glass-hover active:bg-glass-active`
- Selected card: add `ring-1 ring-accent/40 bg-glass-active`
- AI insight blocks: `glass-panel` + `border border-accent/20`, icon inside `rounded-lg bg-accent/20`

## Typography

System font stack (Tailwind default) with `antialiased` on `body`.
OpenType features: `'cv02', 'cv03', 'cv04', 'cv11'` on body.

### Scale

| Context | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Page title / hero | `text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight` |
| Section title | `text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight` or `text-xl font-semibold` |
| Section label | `text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-widest text-glass-text-dim` |
| Body text | `text-sm text-glass-text` or `text-glass-text-muted` |
| Stat value | `text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-white` |
| Micro label | `text-[10px]` or `text-[9px]` |
| Chat bubble | `text-[13px] leading-relaxed` |

### Rules

- Use `uppercase tracking-widest` for category/section labels
- Use `tabular-nums` on numeric displays
- Headings use `tracking-tight`; labels use `tracking-wider` or `tracking-widest`
- Brand name: `mAIcoach` with `<span className="text-accent">AI</span>`

## Layout

### Page structure

- Root layout: full viewport, `bg-mesh` decorative div, `Providers` wrapper
- Dashboard: single column, `max-w-6xl mx-auto`, `px-4 sm:px-6 py-6`, `gap-6`
- Home / landing: centered column, `max-w-3xl mx-auto`, full-height centering

### Responsive approach

Mobile-first. Only `sm:` and `lg:` breakpoints are used (no `md:` / `xl:`).

Common patterns:
- `flex-col` then `sm:flex-row`
- `px-4 sm:px-6`
- `gap-2 sm:gap-3 lg:gap-4`
- Coach panel: full-width `left-4 right-4` on mobile, `sm:w-[380px]` anchored bottom-right on desktop

### Grids

| Context | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Metric cards | `grid grid-cols-3 gap-2 sm:gap-3 lg:gap-4` |
| Tab bar | `grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 p-1` |
| Day selector | `grid grid-cols-7` |
| Stat pairs | `grid grid-cols-2 gap-3` |

## Navigation

No sidebar. Top header with brand, then a segmented tab bar.

Tab bar: `glass-panel grid grid-cols-3 gap-1 p-1` containing `Link` elements.
- Active: `bg-accent/20 text-white shadow-sm rounded-xl`
- Inactive: `text-glass-text-muted hover:text-white hover:bg-glass-hover rounded-xl`

## Buttons

| Variant | Classes |
|---------|---------|
| Primary CTA | `rounded-lg bg-accent px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow-lg transition hover:brightness-110 glow-accent` |
| FAB / orb | `rounded-full bg-accent shadow-lg transition-transform hover:scale-110 active:scale-95` |
| Ghost / close | `rounded-lg p-1 text-glass-text-muted transition-colors hover:bg-glass-hover hover:text-white` |
| Icon button | `h-9 w-9 rounded-xl` + bg/text per variant |
| Disabled | `disabled:opacity-20` |

## Badges / Tags

- Activity type: `rounded-md bg-accent/15 px-2 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-accent`
- Suggestion chip: `rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accent/10 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-medium text-accent hover:bg-accent/20`
- Zone/metric colors: use inline `style={{ color }}` for dynamic values

## Charts (Recharts)

### General rules

- Wrap in `glass-panel p-4` with `ResponsiveContainer` inside
- Axes: `stroke="rgba(255,255,255,0.15)"`, tick fill `rgba(255,255,255,0.35)`, `fontSize: 11`
- No tick lines, no axis lines
- Tooltips: `rounded-lg border border-glass-border bg-[#1a1830] px-3 py-2 text-xs shadow-xl`
- Dot: `dot={false}` on lines/areas; use `activeDot` with `stroke="#1a1830"`

### Area charts (streams)

- Linear gradient fill: top `stopOpacity={0.3}`, bottom `stopOpacity={0.02}`
- `strokeWidth={2}`
- Chart height: `h-48`

### Bar charts (weekly)

- `radius={[4, 4, 0, 0]}`, `maxBarSize={36}`
- Height: `h-32`
- Per-bar fill via data property

### Composed charts (fitness/form)

- Height: 240px
- Reference line at y=0 dashed
- Area fill for TSB (green), solid Line for CTL, dashed Line for ATL (`strokeDasharray="6 4"`)

## Icons

Inline SVG (Heroicons-style paths). No icon library import.
- `stroke="currentColor"`, `fill="none"`, `viewBox="0 0 24 24"`
- `strokeWidth={2}` (occasionally 1.8 or 2.5)
- Sizes: `h-3 w-3` (chevrons) up to `h-6 w-6` (orb)
- Color via text utilities: `text-accent`, `text-glass-text-dim`, `text-white`

## Animations

### CSS (defined in globals.css)

| Class | Keyframes | Duration | Use |
|-------|-----------|----------|-----|
| `coach-orb` | `coach-breathe` | 3s infinite | Orb shadow pulse |
| `coach-orb-ring` | `coach-ring-pulse` | 3s infinite | Ring scale/fade |
| `coach-panel-enter` | `coach-panel-appear` | 0.25s ease-out | Panel slide-up + scale |
| `coach-thinking span` | `coach-dot-bounce` | 1.4s staggered | Thinking dots |

### Tailwind transitions

- Default: `transition` or `transition-colors`, `transition-all`
- Duration: `duration-200` (most), `duration-300`, `duration-700 ease-out` (progress bars)
- Hover transforms: `hover:scale-110`, `active:scale-95`
- Rotate: `transition-transform duration-200` + conditional `rotate-180` (chevrons)
- Ping: `animate-ping` on active voice button

## Shadows

| Context | Pattern |
|---------|---------|
| Basic card | `shadow-sm` |
| Panel / modal | `shadow-2xl` |
| Tooltip | `shadow-xl` |
| Accent glow | `.glow-accent` class (defined in CSS) |
| Inline glow | `shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(99,102,241,0.4)]` for accent highlights |

## Coach Panel Pattern

Floating panel, fixed positioned:
- Mobile: `bottom-4 left-4 right-4`
- Desktop: `sm:left-auto sm:bottom-6 sm:right-6 sm:w-[380px]`
- Shell: `rounded-2xl border border-glass-border bg-[#0c0a1a]/95 shadow-2xl backdrop-blur-xl`
- Max height: `min(60vh, 520px)`
- Sections divided by `border-t border-glass-border/50`

### Chat bubbles

- Coach: `border-l-2 border-accent/40 bg-glass text-glass-text`, with "Coach" label in `text-[8px] uppercase tracking-widest text-accent`
- User: `bg-accent/20 text-white`
- Both: `rounded-2xl px-3 py-2 max-w-[85%]`

## Spacing Conventions

| Context | Value |
|---------|-------|
| Page-level vertical | `gap-6` or `space-y-5` |
| Section internal | `p-4` or `p-5` |
| Between cards | `gap-2 sm:gap-3 lg:gap-4` |
| Tight groups (chips, inputs) | `gap-1.5` or `gap-2` |
| Micro adjustments | `mt-0.5`, `mt-1`, `mb-3` |

## Border Radius Conventions

| Context | Class |
|---------|-------|
| Orb, dots, progress bars | `rounded-full` |
| Coach panel, chat bubbles | `rounded-2xl` |
| Tab links, inputs, icon buttons | `rounded-xl` |
| CTA buttons, icon containers | `rounded-lg` |
| Activity badge | `rounded-md` |
| Glass panel / elevated (CSS) | `1rem` |
| Glass card (CSS) | `0.75rem` |

## Anti-Patterns (DO NOT)

- Do NOT add a light mode or theme toggle
- Do NOT use `bg-white`, `text-slate-*`, `border-slate-*` or any light-theme classes
- Do NOT import an icon library (lucide, heroicons package) -- use inline SVG
- Do NOT install shadcn/ui -- use the glass panel system
- Do NOT create new panel/card CSS classes -- use the three existing tiers
- Do NOT hard-code colors in TSX without first checking if a `@theme` token exists
- Do NOT use `md:` or `xl:` breakpoints -- stick to `sm:` and `lg:`
- Do NOT add scrollbars -- use `scrollbar-hide` class where overflow is needed
- Do NOT use emojis in the UI (except the rest-day face icon)

## Component Structure

Components live in `components/` (not `src/components/`). Pages in `app/`.

| Folder | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| `components/dashboard/` | Workout, week, chart, metric components |
| `components/form/` | Training pulse (gauge, recovery, fitness chart) |
| `components/coach/` | AI coach orb, panel, provider |
| `components/layout/` | Navigation (tab bar) |
| `components/providers/` | Context providers (Convex) |

### Component conventions

- Export named functions (not default exports) for components
- Pages use `export default function PageName()` (Next.js convention)
- Props interfaces defined above the component, suffix `Props`
- All props use `Readonly<Props>` wrapper
- Return type annotated as `ReactNode`
- `'use client'` directive only when needed (state, effects, event handlers)
- Internal sub-components (like `CardContent`, `MessageBubble`) stay in the same file, not exported

## Input Styling

Text inputs: `rounded-xl bg-glass px-3 py-2 text-sm text-white placeholder-glass-text-dim outline-none ring-1 ring-glass-border transition-shadow focus:ring-accent/40`

## Status / Loading States

- Thinking: three dots (`h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent`) with `coach-thinking` animation + "Thinking..." text
- Listening: `ring-1 ring-accent/60` on input, `animate-ping` on mic button, "Listening..." placeholder
- Disabled: `disabled:opacity-20`
- Empty state: centered muted text `text-xs text-glass-text-dim`
- Rest day: circular icon + muted copy (no skeleton/spinner patterns yet)
